{"data":{"site":{"meta":{"title":"Yentsen Liu","description":"Interface/Empowerment/Democracy Design Portfolio by Yentsen Liu","url":"https://yentsenliu.com","author":"Yentsen Liu","twitter":"ansinlau","adsense":""}},"post":{"id":"ea5196be-c9b1-507e-a93a-cda77f2f5996","html":"<h2>Background</h2>\n<p>The world is currently suffering a decline of democracy. User interface and experience have an unevenly important impact on this ongoing crisis. The digital democratic communication is truly one of the most prominent types of practice which have a great diversity within, whereas the situations such as filter bubble and echo chamber has also manifested the ubiquitous silos created by bands of like-minded people. As the current researches tends to focus on the impact of the internet and social networking sites, a standoff has emerged: some of them still hold an optimistic view, whilist some others do not. The research has started with the scope and the premise that more detailed examination of the user experience involved in the design and interaction of the websites could provide us more concrete and specific answers. </p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1024px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"the scope of this research\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/scope-6b751f476e98e27389197629ea08fd9c-e49b2.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/scope-6b751f476e98e27389197629ea08fd9c-ddbb0.jpg 500w,\n/static/scope-6b751f476e98e27389197629ea08fd9c-a5e6c.jpg 1000w,\n/static/scope-6b751f476e98e27389197629ea08fd9c-e49b2.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>The scope and the premise of this research</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<p>Kialo and Pol.is are two novel platforms addressing this issue. They both have a growing active community of users. The interactive argument diagrams, which make the communication and demonstration of the opinions possible, are at the core of their user experience.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 35.34777651083238%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Two examples of interactive argument diagram:  Kialo (left) and Pol.is (right)\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/figure-2b4ca21a3df593164e169642ac0a2d2e-7874f.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/figure-2b4ca21a3df593164e169642ac0a2d2e-cf602.jpg 500w,\n/static/figure-2b4ca21a3df593164e169642ac0a2d2e-ec5b1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/figure-2b4ca21a3df593164e169642ac0a2d2e-7874f.jpg 2000w,\n/static/figure-2b4ca21a3df593164e169642ac0a2d2e-b35a9.jpg 3000w,\n/static/figure-2b4ca21a3df593164e169642ac0a2d2e-948c0.jpg 3508w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Two examples of interactive argument diagram:  <a href=\"https://www.kialo.com/does-pineapple-belong-on-pizza-10104/10104.0=10104.1/=10104.1\" target=\"blank\">Kialo</a> (left) and <a href=\"https://mydem0cracy.ca\" target=\"blank\">Pol.is</a> (right). Click the links to see the examples.</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<h2>So, what research I want to do?</h2>\n<p>Taking the feasible scale of a masterâ€™s thesis into account, the research is thus narrowed down to the core: <strong>How to design interactive argument diagram for democratic communication?</strong></p>\n<p>I would like to make interactive prototypes of argument diagrams and to track the behavioral changes of the citizens during the process of communication. The main focus is twofold: </p>\n<ol>\n<li>How do the interface of argument diagram make behavioral changes of the citizens as well as changes to their cognition and attitude; </li>\n<li>How to develop a theoretical framework for evaluating the advantages and the disadvantages with the values of democracy. </li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1024px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"the framework of the research\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/diagram-62d1a193880b4d313ac15b5d0046fe2a-e49b2.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/diagram-62d1a193880b4d313ac15b5d0046fe2a-ddbb0.jpg 500w,\n/static/diagram-62d1a193880b4d313ac15b5d0046fe2a-a5e6c.jpg 1000w,\n/static/diagram-62d1a193880b4d313ac15b5d0046fe2a-e49b2.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>How to design interactive argument diagram for democratic communication?</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<h2>Expected outcome</h2>\n<p>The expected outcomes of this research are listed below:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A theoretical framework on what democratic values of design should be and how to operationalize it in an empirical and constructive design research </li>\n<li>An exploration on how to involve behavior tracking techniques and quantitative analysis in human-centered design research and experimental political sciences</li>\n<li>A design proposal of argument diagramming for a better democratic outcome</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Help wanted</h2>\n<p>This is a work-in-progress project, and everything will be updated regularly here. Currently, I am initializing it and <strong>actively looking for external collaborators, adivsors, and a possible thesis worker position. If you are interested in this plan, please do not hesitant to contact me at yen-tsen.liu[AT]aalto.fi</strong></p>\n<p>Last update: 2018-11-14.</p>","frontmatter":{"layout":"post","title":"Designing Diagram for Democracy","path":"/master-thesis-plan/","category":"design for democracy","tags":["Digital Democracy","User Interface","Exmperimental Political Science"],"description":"How to design interactive argument diagram for democratic communication? This is Yentsen Liu's ongoing master's thesis work at Aalto University, Finland.","date":"2018/11/14","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":500,"height":357,"src":"/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-7f380.jpg","srcSet":"/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-7f380.jpg 1x,\n/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-b4bc2.jpg 1.5x,\n/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-ac12b.jpg 2x","srcWebp":"/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-e6ca4.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-e6ca4.webp 1x,\n/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-4bf37.webp 1.5x,\n/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-0c5e8.webp 2x"},"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3987012987012988,"src":"/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-c391d.jpg","srcSet":"/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-41c10.jpg 200w,\n/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-df9ca.jpg 400w,\n/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-c391d.jpg 800w,\n/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-e26e4.jpg 1077w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{}}